14 c. The amount or value of the property;
15 d. The last address of the apparent owner, if known to the holder;
16 e. If the holder sells, issues, or provides to others for sale or issue in this state
17 traveler's checks, money orders, or similar instruments, other than third-party
18 bank checks, on which the holder is directly liable, a record of the instruments
19 while they remain outstanding indicating the state and date of issue; and
20 f. Records of items that were not reported as unclaimed sufficient to determine
21 whether the holder has complied with this chapter.
